---
title: Seared Honey-Garlic Sausages with Springtime Veggie Succotash and Israeli Couscous
description: Succotash is a hearty Southern vegetable dish that traditionally contains corn and lima beans. We're switching up the beans for edamame, and tossing it up with bell peppers and Israeli couscous! Seared honey-garlic sausage pairs perfectly with this vegetable medley.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/seared-honey-garlic-sausages-29d56509.jpg
